<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, March 23 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock Exchange
National-100 Index closed at 4,315.09 on Tuesday, down 1.18
points, or 0.02 percent, from Monday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The trading was active with the turnover reaching over 105
trillion Turkish Liras (about 290 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index dropped 36.30 points, or 0.63 percent, to
close at 5,698.48 points, the services index fell 4.89 points, or
0.08 percent, to close at 5,558.08 points while the industrial
index rose 43.38 points, or 1.52 percent, to close at 2,946.86
points. 
