<HEADLINE> Russia Calls for Resuming Peace Talks on Kosovo </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, March 24 (Xinhua) -- Russian Foreign Minister Igor
Ivanov Thursday called on all sides involved in the Kosovo crisis
to resume peace talks immediately.
</P>
