down 15.33 points, or 1.80 percent, to 835.58, while the H-share
index dropped 8.99 points, or 2.32 percent, to 378.43.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong stocks opened 1.82 percent lower and closed the
morning session 2.62 percent lower at 10,751.46 Wednesday.
