shedding 40 cents to close at 19.90 Singapore dollars. DBS F and
OCBC F lost 30 cents to finish at 12.50 and 11.40 Singapore
dollars respectively. CityDev retreated 25 cents to end at 7.80
Singapore dollars.
</P>
