increasing management difficulties for the SDB in recent years.
</P>
<P>
They pointed out that the Zhengzhou Branch will introduce more
credit and loan services to support local economic development.
</P>
<P>
The SBD will assume control of 20 branch banks formerly
operated by the China Investment Bank.  
